            <div type="commentary">
                <head>Commentary</head>
                <p>Line 1· Perhaps the words τόπῳ καλῷ, 'in a fair place'.</p>
                <p>Line 2: a name, Εὐ]α̣ν̣γέλου, or a reference to messengers or angels?</p>
                <p>Given the uncertainties of interpretation, the main value of this text is to show that at Martuba there were people who 
                    continued to inscribe in Greek much later than the community at Kharsa is known to have done. </p>
            </div>
